IN THE NEWS 





















BlueMountain Capital Management Continues Buildout of Equities Strategies;  Lance Rosen Joins in New Head of Equities Role
NEW YORK, JUNE 26, 2017 – BlueMountain Capital Management, LLC (“BlueMountain”), a private diversified alternative asset management firm with $22 billion in assets under management, continues to build and diversify its equities business, with the addition of Lance Rosen as Head of Equities effective July 10, 2017. 
The full article is attached here.

Congratulations to Marina Lutova Meyers and Sarah Dahan on their inclusion in Hedge Fund Journal’s 50 Leading Women in Hedge Funds 2017.
May 23, 2017
We are thrilled that Marina and Sarah have been recognized, and are proud of BlueMountain’s record of promoting talented women into leadership positions. 
The full report is attached here.




 




