BlueMountain Capital Management LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg










































  





















































































July 26, 2017 11:50 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of BlueMountain Capital Management LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
BlueMountain Capital Management LLC is a privately owned hedge fund manager. It provides its services to pooled investment vehicles operating as private investment funds and institutional accounts typically operating as single-investor limited partnerships or foreign companies. The firm manages separate client-focused portfolios. It invests in public equity, fixed income, and alternative investment markets across the globe. For its alternative investments, the firm invests in long/short credit, long/short equity, distressed and special situations, CLOs, asset-backed securities, synthetic structured credit, mortgages, commercial real estate, volatility, convertibles and index/bond basis strat...
BlueMountain Capital Management LLC is a privately owned hedge fund manager. It provides its services to pooled investment vehicles operating as private investment funds and institutional accounts typically operating as single-investor limited partnerships or foreign companies. The firm manages separate client-focused portfolios. It invests in public equity, fixed income, and alternative investment markets across the globe. For its alternative investments, the firm invests in long/short credit, long/short equity, distressed and special situations, CLOs, asset-backed securities, synthetic structured credit, mortgages, commercial real estate, volatility, convertibles and index/bond basis strategies. It employs combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis to create its portfolios. BlueMountain Capital Management LLC was founded in 2003 and is based in New York, New York.
Detailed Description


