Back to AMG AffiliatesBlueMountain Capital Management, LLCInvestment DisciplineBlueMountain Capital Management (“BlueMountain”) is a diversified alternative asset manager that uses an interdisciplinary approach to identify opportunities stemming from artificial investor segmentation, behavioral biases and idiosyncratic events. With a heritage in the credit markets, its multi-strategy platform now includes investments in credit, distressed, equity, structured finance & real estate as well as arbitrage and technical strategies. BlueMountain’s investment team operates in a highly integrated manner, with risk management as a key element of the Company’s investment process.The FirmBlueMountain was founded in 2003 by Andrew Feldstein, Chief Executive Officer and Co-Chief Investment Officer, and Stephen Siderow, Co-President. BlueMountain has a team of more than 250 professionals. The Company is based in New York and has an office in London.Contact Information280 Park Avenue, 12th FloorNew York, NY 10017+1 (212) 905-3900 5 Hanover Square, 3rd  
FloorLondon W1S 1HE United Kingdomwww.bluemountaincapital.com




