 BlueMountain Capital Management Appoints Summer Jarratt to Senior West Coast Marketing Role 
         










    










 






 











 









BlueMountain Capital Management Appoints Summer Jarratt to Senior West Coast Marketing Role

		  --Move designed to support BlueMountain's growing momentum among institutional investors in the Western United States --
		

Oct 06, 2015, 09:38 ET
		  		  					
						 from   BlueMountain Capital Management, LLC 











 
















































 

 




















 


NEW YORK, Oct. 6, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- In a move geared to support its growth efforts in the Western United States, BlueMountain Capital Management, a private investment firm with over $22 billion in assets under management, announced today it has appointed Summer Jarratt as Client Advisor overseeing its West Coast business development and client service.  Ms. Jarratt's hire is designed to enhance BlueMountain's growing West Coast investor base and build on the momentum of recently secured agreements for new mandates with the Orange County (CA) Employees Retirement System and the New Mexico Public Employees Retirement Association (NM PERA).  Ms. Jarratt will report to Noam Leslau, BlueMountain Capital Management's US Head of Client Advisory.
Based in Los Angeles, Ms. Jarratt will implement business development strategies to attract institutional investors, family offices and retail platforms with a focus on the Western United States.  She will further play an important role in managing existing LP relationships and informing BlueMountain's product development strategy.  
"Summer is a seasoned professional with granular knowledge of the challenges and opportunities that can be found in partnering with US institutional allocators," said Noam Leslau. "She comes to us with an established network and is extremely well-versed in customized, high-end client service.  Summer will be instrumental in increasing our growing West Coast footprint and further establishing our position as a premier institutional asset manager."
Prior to joining BlueMountain, Ms. Jarratt co-managed client relationships and business development for Empyrean Capital Partners, a private investment firm with over $2 billion in assets under management. Ms. Jarratt relies on over 15 years of total experience inclusive of Empyrean as well as work as a business manager for Los Angeles-based Green Dot Public Schools, five years as Vice President of Client Relations for Chilton Investment Company and three years dating back to 2001 in various roles with Cambridge Associates. 
"The opportunity to join BlueMountain is extremely exciting," said Ms. Jarratt. "The firm's unparalleled ability to find opportunities across capital structures has resulted in its much deserved reputation for sophistication and excellence.  I am thrilled to be joining BlueMountain and helping to further raise its brand awareness across the Western United States." 
About BlueMountain Capital Management, LLC
BlueMountain Capital Management, LLC ("BlueMountain") is a leading private investment firm managing $22 billion of assets. BlueMountain's large and diverse team of professionals in New York and London are supported by the firm's institutionalized and proprietary infrastructure, including specialized operations and risk management technology.
Media Contact:
Doug Hesney doug@dukaspr.com 212-704-7385 
 SOURCE  BlueMountain Capital Management, LLC  




  

